# Strict UI Architecture Rules

- DO NOT hardcode width/height in leaf components.
- Every component must accept className and forward ...props.
- Always preserve parent container layout contract (flex/grid/overflow).
- Keep formatting deterministic with Biome.
- Ban: w-[...], h-[...], bg-[#...], @apply (unless spec.md exception).
- Add or maintain Breadcrumb + JSDoc metadata tags in each component.
- Before editing, consult docs/ui-map.ascii.txt and docs/spec.md.
